snippet.title: Tadpole Treble Launch Trailer (May 6th on Steam)
snippet.description:
Add to Steam Wishlist already! Good Gosh, what are you waiting for?
http://store.steampowered.com/app/354400/

Hey there, sport! Sick of wasting time doing things like mowing the lawn, shaving your legs, and sending telegrams to grandma? Then play Tadpole Treble, a musical adventure that comes out in May 6th, 2016 (AD)!

Tadpole Treble is probably the greatest game of all time. Any time spent not playing this game has been utterly wasted--it will surprise your spouse, concern your neighbors, energize your dog and explode your hamster. Features not only a piranha, but also lines.

Brought to you from the demented mind behind beloved webcomic Brawl in the Family, and his arguably more demented brother.
